Peru’s Ex-Economy Minister Comes Out of Hiding, Canal N Says

-- B y   J o h n   Q u i g l e y
-- 
2011-04-13T23:18:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/peru-s-ex-economy-minister-comes-out-of-hiding-canal-n-says.html
Peru ’s former Economy Minister Juan Carlos Hurtado came out of hiding 10 years after he was charged
with embezzlement and corrupting public officials, Canal N
reported.  Hurtado, who implemented a series of measures to stabilize
Peru’s economy to stem hyperinflation in 1990, turned himself in
to the authorities today, the Lima-based broadcaster reported
without saying how it obtained the information.  To contact the reporters on this story:
John Quigley in Lima at 
